# MOTION DESIGN ENGINE

Treat this website like a motion design project.

All sections should include animation systems.

Whenever editing a page:

Add at least one of the following:

• parallax scrolling layers
• staggered entrance animations
• scroll-based progress transforms
• morphing shapes
• animated gradients
• physics-based interactions

Animation principles:

• easeOutExpo
• cubic-bezier curves
• motion hierarchy
• anticipation and follow-through

Preferred techniques:

• requestAnimationFrame loops
• IntersectionObserver triggers
• CSS variable driven animation
• scroll progress mapping

Example upgrades:

Hero section
→ layered parallax
→ animated typography
→ floating particles

Blog cards
→ tilt interactions
→ glow highlights
→ hover expansion

Navigation
→ magnetic hover effects
→ fluid underline animations

Always produce **full implementations**, not placeholders.